            <biogHist>
                <p>Norman MacIver or Tormod Clèireach was church officer on the Isle of Harris while
                    Reverend Aulay MacAulay was minister there. It is said that he came from the
                    Isle of Lewis with Mr MacAulay when he took up his charge in Harris and that
                    MacIver was buried next to him in the church.</p>
